title: Unlocked skin is locked
body: I had purchased urf warwick with blue essence after patch 8.2 the skin became unlocked again can i get help or a refund for that? i love that skin but sucks i cant pick it anymore

replies.body: You might be looking at the wrong skin, there are actually two types of Urf skins for Warwick. The one you bought was Urfwick, and the one you see that's locked is Urf the Manatee. Double check your collection for the other skin, you still have it unlocked ^_^
